<!doctype html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-PsH8R72JQ3SOdhVi3uxftmaW6Vc51MKb0q5P2rRUpPvrszuE4W1povHYgTpBfshb"
        crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='../mfStyles.css' />
    <title> Movie Finder </title>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm  navbar-dark">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Francisco Arroyo</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="mfContainer">
        <h1 class="mainHeader">Movie Finder</h1>
        <p class="pInfo">A web app for movie searches. Let's find you a movie to watch. </p>
        <a class="mkLink" href="https://fa-movie-finder.herokuapp.com">See It Live Here</a>
        <div class="upperContainer">
            <div class="builtInfo">
                <p>Built with:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Express</li>
                    <li>ReactJS</li>
                    <li>NodeJS</li>
                    <li>Redux</li>
                    <li>OMDB API</li>
                    <li>Bootstrap</li>
                    <li>& more...</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <img src="./views/public/mfinder.png" alt="Image of Project">
        </div>
        <div class="imgContainer">
            <img src="./views/public/mfSearch.png" alt="Image of Project">
        </div>
        <div class="signupInfo">
            <p>If you're a Bruce Willis fan you might enter "Die Hard" in the search bar. 
                 On "Go!", an Axios HTTP request is sent to the Online Movie Data Base (OMDB) API,
                  which returns 10 movies based off the search. But which one
                   did you want to watch? </p>
        </div>
        <div class="imgContainer">
            <img src="./views/public/mfdetails.png" alt="Image of Project">
        </div>
        <div class="signupInfo">
            <p>View further details and movie ratings to make your decision. Based on the selected 
                movie's id an Axios HTTP request to OBDM API retrieves further movie details for display.
                Not the movie you wanted to watch, click "Go Back" and start a new search!

            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div id="footer" class="container-fluid">
        <p class="py-2 pr-2 text-muted text-right footer">&copy;2018 Francisco Arroyo </p>
    </div>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.6/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0-beta.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>